these men do with the people they arrest?â

âWhy, they carry them off in their train,â Monsieur de Carnavant
replied. âThey no doubt consider them excellent hostages.â

âAh!â the old woman rejoined, in a strange tone.

Then she again thoughtfully watched the curious scene of panic around
