âItâs they that we shall have to reduce to impotence if they persist in
betraying the country!â he cried. âAnd what do they intend to do with
the citizens whom they arrest?â

âWhat do they intend to do with them? Why, they will shoot them in the
lowest dungeons of the prison, of course,â replied Macquart, with a
hoarse laugh. And as the young man, stupefied with horror, looked at
