faint whisper told his wife of an idea that had just occurred to him.

âOh! no, no,â Felicite murmured, with a shudder. âThat would be too
cruel.â

âWell,â he resumed, âbut you want to spread consternation among the
inhabitants! They would take me seriously, if what I told you should
